creator: SkyDivers
descriptionHtml:
Immerse yourself in the world of space with the Planet Earth 3D app.

Impressive high-resolution 4K textures, stars and the Milky Way allow you to plunge into the mysterious atmosphere of the solar system.

The application allows not only to monitor the current position of the Earth in the solar system, but also to control them. Take control of the sun, moon and earth in your hands. A convenient interface allows you to set up brightness, contrast that is comfortable for you, and choose a pleasant palette of colors for yourself.

With the Planet Earth 3D application you will never miss the necessary phase of the moon and you can enjoy the atmosphere of a mysterious and incomprehensible space in real time right on your phone.

Feauteres:

High quality 3D live wallpaper with current position Earth & Moon in space!
4K textures.
Parallax effect.
Current Moon phase.
Real position int solar system.
